{"id":232487833,"title":"校園隨筆 #2 ポッキー","content":"11月11日。以前在台灣過光棍節，\n現在來日本改過ポッキーの日。\n\n今天（雖然晚了一天）被同學呼喚到販賣部，\n說是一次買2盒pocky就能兌換一支pocky空氣棒。\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsol.jpg\n照片取自Google圖片\n\n這不是我們學校的販賣部，但大致就是這種風情。\n\n為了湊盒數，買了一盒冬季限定的巧克力口味，當作微積分課的零食，和同學們分掉了。還不錯吃。\n\n同學吃完不忘吐槽一句\n\n「お前一日遅れじゃん笑」\n『別にいいじゃん笑』\n\n———————\n\n這樣的行銷手法蠻不錯的。實際上也一定有不少學生為了氣球去消費。若不是怕晚了一天還拿著一根pocky引人注目，其實我也想要一支呢 ( ´▽｀)","excerpt":"11月11日。以前在台灣過光棍節，現在來日本改過ポッキーの日。今天（雖然晚了一天）被同學呼喚到販賣部，說是一次買2盒pocky就能兌換一支pocky空氣棒。照片取自Google圖片，這不是我們學校的販","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ee51d6cd-ad7e-4d73-b79a-3ce32ea7798b","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-12T10:24:59.765Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-12T10:24:59.765Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":19,"tags":[],"topics":["Pocky","1111","日本留學","日本生活","廢文"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"日本生活","forumAlias":"japan_life","school":"我是住在東京的大學生","department":"kaiw_inut","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":18},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsol.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"df521564-6f10-4b97-9965-aa3b7e1e148d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsoll.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsoll.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsoll.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-12T10:24:59.765Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-12T10:24:59.765Z"},{"id":"df521564-6f10-4b97-9965-aa3b7e1e148d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsol.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/4ZFNsol","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/4ZFNsoll.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-12T10:24:59.765Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-12T10:24:59.765Z"}